txt.en: Collect Black Númenórean artifacts within The Towers of the Teeth.

While exploring The Towers of the Teeth, you notice some treasures from the lands of Rhûn.

You take it upon yourself to collect samples of these Black Númenórean treasures for the Host of the West.

<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires The Towers of the Teeth: Guardian of the Depths to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
Bring the Black Númenórean artifacts to Candúr
Collect Black Númenórean artifacts within The Towers of the Teeth.
You should collect Black Númenórean artifacts and bring them to Candúr.

While exploring The Towers of the Teeth, you notice some treasures from the lands of Rhûn.

You take it upon yourself to collect samples of these Black Númenórean treasures for the Host of the West.

<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires The Towers of the Teeth: Guardian of the Depths to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>

'These artifacts are extremely interesting. While I do not know what powers they may hold or history they may tell, we should keep them until the battle is won. Perhaps a scholar from Minas Tirith would be able to study them.'
Bring the Black Númenórean artifacts to Candúr
Towers of the Teeth: A Brush with Darkness
